<title>BRIEF-US EPA rules on Enbridge spill recovery plans</title>
<source>Reuters</source>
<date>2010-08-04</date>
<snippet>Aug 4 - Susan Hedman, regional administrator with the US Environmental Protection Agency, to a news conference on the Enbridge Inc oil spill in Marshall ...</snippet>
<content>
        
    
Aug 4 (Reuters) - Susan Hedman, regional administrator with
the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency, to a news conference
on the Enbridge Inc oil spill in Marshall, Michigan:

 * EPA approves Enbridge (ENB.TO) health, safety plan for
Michigan pipe break * approves Enbridge pipeline repair plan, with
modifications * rejects Enbridge sampling and analysis plans, with
comments * approves Enbridge oil recovery and containment plan * downstream impact plan under review * waste treatment and disposal plan approved with
modifications
 (Reporting by Jeffrey Jones; editing by Rob Wilson)




